message: Keep changing the suites until you get either hearts or diamonds than combine your ingredients and increase the number.
Try a couple until you get a better number and then continue to use the "double" card for as long as possible.
Sometimes there is a common sense combination.
Sometimes you only need to use the "tools"

Try and combine ingredients that would actually go well together like paint and cardboard etc. Avoid framing anything since that seems to lower your score. Don't combine everything either. Just make a few separate crafts and submit the score.
Newspaper is a great idea.
I generally tried to increase the numbers until I got a high number and then I did suit swapper to make the two ingredients the same suit then I finally combined them.
watch the descriptions as they change for clues.
DONT PICK THE GIRAFFE FIRST, IT WILL GO NEGATIVE SCORE. I think the growth serum and the mutation catalysts generally allowed you to beef up your score.
The only thing I didn't try was combining actual animals. Individual animals combined with ingredients didn't seem to lead to a positive outcome.
I would generally try to stick to a single ingredient (peppers and apples easiest) and just cook those first without combining them.
I combined the items for a big increase. use the tools too much and you'll go negative.

I would generally just try to make a pleasureful arts and crafts project and don't overthink it too much. There didn't seem to be a rhyme or reason to this other than just combining ingredients and tools based on typical order in a craft project.
Don't filter anything.

I would not combine all ingredients first, I would instead first use the vial or wand on a single ingredient and go from there. Also I noticed applying any tool to the Frog Leg results in a negative score so avoid that if possible.
The water just seems to soak the items instead of washing them. Make more than one dish! Combine the dishes that make sense to.
Try and combine things the way you would in real life. Like mushrooms and stove and onions and knife etc.
Combine the animals.
I have no clue.

You have to try to combine the cards to get the highest score, and put the cards on the tools. Try to combine separtely before combining together.
The only tool that gains points for  me was the wand after combining all ingredients.
Use the suit swapper repeatedly to get to the hearts suit.
Combine actual ingredients that you would need for actual food.

Combine the knife with the pineapple, coconut, carrot, and ginger. Combine the stove with the raw meat and butter.
